# HITL Checkpoints

## Dev HITL (require user approval before implementing)

- Changing tier agent matrix (`agent_registry.py`)
- Changing default LLM models in `defaults.yaml`
- Changing `TOKEN_BUDGET` defaults or control profile ceilings
- Removing or bypassing QA / admin loops

## Runtime HITL (built into Flow)

| Gate | Trigger |
|------|---------|
| Requirements | After intake — approve / edit / cancel |
| Workflow | After Mermaid plan generated |
| Budget | Token usage exceeds profile ceiling |

Profiles: `conservative` (more gates), `standard`, `aggressive` (fewer gates).
